    ///
    /// Supported modes:
    /// - `0x01000000000000000000...`: Single batch. Does not support optional `opData`.
    /// - `0x01000000000078210001...`: Single batch. Supports optional `opData`.
    /// - `0x01000000000078210002...`: Batch of batches.
    ///
